## Error Handling

```ruby
begin
  result = client.some_api.some_method
rescue {{pascalCase meta.clientName}}::SDKError => e
  puts "Error #{e.status}: #{e.message} (#{e.code})"
  puts "Request ID: #{e.request_id}" if e.request_id

  if e.rate_limited?
    sleep 1
    retry
  end

  raise
end
```

